L,NULL,'\r\n',56),(1,'StudentHome2007',2,NULL,'Messages for students on placement 2007','<B>First Visit Online Form</B><BR><BR>\r\n\r\nA review of the online forms being used to assess your placement is being conducted this year.<BR><BR>\r\n\r\nYour first visit form, when completed, will NOT have any of the radio buttons selected. Instead feedback, including a grade, will be provided in the field labelled \'Comments on and for the Student\'.<BR><BR>\r\n\r\nAs a result of this, the Assessment Information listed below your timeline will not be applicable. Do not worry about a zero appearing for your first visit.<BR><BR><BR>\r\n\r\n\r\n<B>Annual Placement Student Competition Launched</B><BR><BR>\r\n \r\nThe  competition is for new 2007/8 placement students, who are asked to compete to become our new \"bloggers\".  The winners will be asked to write three 300-word \"blogs\" about their ongoing placement experiences, over the course of the academic year, with payment of Â£200 for!
