 \r\n\r\nI would like to have the opportunity to work in your business,
 becoming\r\ninvolved in maintenance, testing and configuration.  I know my hardware and\r\nsoftware skills would be of benefit to me in this work role.  I particularly\r\nenjoy the networking and systems design element of computing and would like\r\nto take an active part in an IT business.\r\n\r\nThrough my work programmes and part-time employment I have gained experience\r\nin public relations and communications.  I have also been able to manage my\r\nresponsibilities within different working environments.  I have developed\r\ntime-management, teamwork and problem solving techniques both within my\r\nstudies and work situations.  The responsibilities I undertook allowed me to\r\nwork on my own initiative.  My part-time employment has allowed me to\r\nincrease my understanding and knowledge of technological advances in sales\r\nprocedures.  I am occasionally appointed to carry out supervisory\r\nresponsibilities.  Through my volunteer work in the community I have\r\nenhanc!
