 ,NULL,'Messages for students unplaced 2008 JN','<B>This announcement applies to students in the Jordanstown-based Computing School only.</B><BR>\r\n\r\nStudents whose CV does not pass the minimum quality threshold will NOT be able to use their CV to apply for jobs via the PDSystem.  If your CV is in this category you will need to make an appointment to meet with Edwin Curran, bringing along a paper copy of your CV.  While every effort will be made facilitate  you there will be an unavoidable delay.  The date when your CV meets the minimum quality threshold will be noted.<BR><BR>\r\n',65),(1,'StudentHomeRequired2008',1,'','SEME Student Home Required 2008','<h4>ANNOUNCEMENTS for SEME STUDENTS who REQUIRE PLACEMENT in 2008</h4>\r\n<p>(This announcement last update: Mon 10 Mar 08 12:30)<br /><br /><strong>Welcome</strong><br />Welcome to the OPUS Web Site. Here you will see vacancy promotions, your applications (bids), the status of your bid, company information, frequent annou!
